—ЩLarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/exec.mdЩ@004fc5890523a08387e1256299f20874d6dfdd219c572fd21c7f31e7978eaf04«title: exec‘ҐNotesЩјOn Unix-based systems, the current process is replaced with the command.

On Windows based systems, Nushell will wait for the command to finish and then exit with the command's exit code.
’ђђЩдTitle: title: exec
Path: Notes
Content:
On Unix-based systems, the current process is replaced with the command.

On Windows based systems, Nushell will wait for the command to finish and then exit with the command's exit code.
